Randomly picked dataset from the Illinois area from 1979.

WD1979.Rd

Data from the Illinois area from one point from the 32km grid from NOAA from 1979.

Format

A data frame with 365 observations of the following 9 variables.

year

Year (numeric; always 1979)

month

Month (not available; can be computed from JD)

day

Day of the month (not available; can be computed from year and JD)

JD

Day of the year ([1, 365]; numeric)

maxTemp

Maximum temperature (degrees Celsius; numeric).

minTemp

Minimum temperature (degrees Celsius; numeric).

SolarR

Solar radiation (MJ / m^2; numeric).

PotEv

Potential evaporation (kg / m^2 ~ mm; numeric)

precip

Precipitation (kg / m^2 ~ mm; numeric)

Source

http://www.noaa.gov/

Examples


data(WD1979)
summary(WD1979)
